/* √Ę‚ÄĚ‚ā¨√Ę‚ÄĚ‚ā¨ Base Reset √Ę‚ÄĚ‚ā¨√Ę‚ÄĚ‚ā¨ */
.cr-root *, .cr-root *::before, .cr-root *::after {
  box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0;
}

.cr-root {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 20px;
  background: transparent;
  min-height: auto;
  font-family: inherit;
  color: #0a2540;
}

.cr-hero {
  background: linear-gradient(92deg, #0a2540 0%, #0b6c67 52%, #0db98f 100%);
  border-radius: 20px;
  padding: 20px 26px;
  color: #fff;
  box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(10, 37, 64, 0.22);
}

.cr-hero-main {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 24px;
}

.cr-hero-brand {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 14px;
}

.cr-hero-icon {
  width: 52px;
  height: 52px;
  border-radius: 15px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-size: 22px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.cr-hero-copy h1 {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: clamp(18px, 1.8vw, 26px);
  line-height: 1.1;
  color: #fff;
}

.cr-hero-copy p {
  margin: 4px 0 0;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
}

.cr-hero-center {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}

.cr-hero-stat {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 0 24px;
}

.cr-hero-stat-num {
  font-size: clamp(22px, 2vw, 32px);
  font-weight: 800;
  line-height: 1;
}

.cr-hero-stat-lbl {
  margin-top: 4px;
  font-size: 11px;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
}

.cr-hero-divider {
  width: 1px;
  height: 36px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
}

.cr-hero-nav {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: flex-end;
  gap: 8px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 5;
  pointer-events: auto;
}

.cr-nav-pill {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
  height: 40px;
  padding: 0 16px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.28);
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
  color: #fff;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 600;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background 0.18s;
}

.cr-nav-pill:hover {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.22);
}

.cr-nav-pill--ai {
  background: linear-gradient(120deg, #7c3aed, #4f46e5);
  border-color: transparent;
  box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.35);
}

.cr-nav-pill--cta {
  background: #fff;
  color: #0a2540;
  border-color: #fff;
  min-width: 148px;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 10px;
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 800;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(10, 37, 64, 0.18);
  position: relative;
  z-index: 40;
  pointer-events: auto;
}

.cr-hero-toolbar {
  margin-top: 16px;
  padding-top: 14px;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 16px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.cr-hero-toolbar-right {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

